    <h1>6 KARA CAFE AND DESSERT BAR</h1>
    <h2></h2>
    <section>
        <a href="/singapore/the-straits-times/textview" title="The Straits Times">The Straits Times</a>
        - <a href="/singapore/the-straits-times/20201004/textview" title="The Straits Times - 2020-10-04"><time>2020-10-04</time></a>
        - <span>LIFE FOOD &amp; DRINK</span>
        - <span role="byline"></span>
    </section>

    <p>With trop­i­cal wall­pa­per on one side of the cafe and oval mir­rors laid out across a pink brick wall on the other, it is hard not to feel like you are out­side of Sin­ga­pore upon step­ping in.</p>
    <p>This veg­e­tar­ian- and pet-friendly cafe serves nu­tri­tion-for­ward foods with ro­bust flavours, such as tofu kale salad and Coco Cashew Grain­bowl. Top off the vir­tu­ous eat­ing by shar­ing a warm skil­let cookie.</p>
    <p>Info: 617 Bukit Timah Road, tel: 6468-8940</p>

